Subject: Re: [T2] Indicator lights (One side) & Brake Lights down 1970

That could be as simple as cleaning your fuses.
Often the end corrode up a bit and the current stops even when they haven't
blown.

This is not uncommon particularly if your windshield leaks as most do.


